Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Harbingers of terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,have you come from the depths of Hell along with this maddening storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite elegantly arranged, l must say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,lf you're one of Blastica's apostles, then you must know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know my name, the man who crushes the darkest of dark itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Baron Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as l'm around,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,l will not allow Crossland to be ravaged at the whim of you followers of Blastica!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honorable Duke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that you, Baron Zeke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Baron Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.94,Note,,0,0,0,,New Legend of Lyon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:54.24,Note,,0,0,0,,New Legend of Lyon Jet-Black Devil
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Baron? Lord Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's me, Polarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here, Lord Baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can keep it down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord Baron is still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But it's already noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord Baron is exhausted after working throughout the night in the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Lony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My... Good morning, Lord Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here to see me, Countess Peauvoir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, call me Polarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You come here every single day for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you go home and stop interrupting my cleaning, Polarine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow-ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,l told you to refer to me as Countess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow-ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hear my troubles, Lord Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,l have to be the unluckiest woman in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband passed away in our second year of marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving this delicate lady to fend for herself alone in this cruel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've told him that about 300 times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,l've only told him that 200 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her speak, Lony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,lt helps her cope in the difficult time she's going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who understands how l feel, Lord Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,l see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Lony, sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you think you could help me out until l arrive at Count Desleen's residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in response to his request?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, about accepting the gracious invitation he's extended to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,An invitation from Count Desleen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,C..Could that mean the new Great Holy Martial Arts Tournament that's about to begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! l knew you'd be asked to participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,l will support you with every fiber of my being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, l don't care to enter the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But l've wanted to meet with the Count for some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But then the Count will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The current head of the famous Desleen family
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,whose influence spreads across Crossland, Rozent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm convinced he's one of Blastica's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That fine gentleman is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what he's plotting by using
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the Great Holy Martial Arts Tournament as a pretense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he invited me, l'll take my time figuring it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's true, nothing tops the greatest view in all of Crossland: the Blue Skies Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm taken aback each time l see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's been the secondary castle of the Count's family for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's rich and single!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, l haven't felt my heart throb this much since my husband passed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, since this is the venue for the Great Holy Martial Arts Tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire country is full of excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, they're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Swordsman of Russelvalley, Baulo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Colas, of the Ocean of Flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and over there's the Duelist of Zayratown, Needham!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Holy Martial Arts Tournament is really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All the famous swordsmen from across the land are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,l have to get their autographs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They call this the Great Holy Martial Arts Tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,lnteresting, looks like it was worth the trip after all, Jokka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the impressive guest list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, most all of the Crossland Council's bigwigs are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,lndeed. l wonder if it's all for the Count to put on quite the large show?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Might you be Lord Zeke of the Balenheim family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,ln the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,l thank you kindly for the gracious invitation you've bestowed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, l'm honored that a warrior of your caliber has come here, Lord Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your presence will certainly make the Great Holy Martial Arts Tournament interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,l, too, am looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't believe you'll be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,l've prepared the line-up appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Fascinating indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The matches begin tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For tonight, try and enjoy yourself as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,lf you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that you, Neris?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,l've been looking for you, Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would have thought we'd meet here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What a politely worded greeting. l'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, you were the only swordsman to have ever bested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,l haven't wasted these long years and months.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,l can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:12:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,l will win our next duel. l swear on my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm looking forward to the matches tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get defeated until we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,lndeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here? You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're up above the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,l met her before l returned to Crossland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was during my travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so just like myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the most dangerous woman in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a swordsman worth fearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, this is Blastica's strongest opponent: Baron Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,l've slain many a warrior to reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all else, l must defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Desleen, is everything going according to plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lady, Baron Zeke is within our midst.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,l've gathered all of the strongest warriors here to the Great Holy Martial Arts Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,l've summoned the three swordsmen from the Death Realm to be his opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,l've also prepared something which will annihilate all of Crossland's warriors in one fell swoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that to the Lady's liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, now listen to me, Desleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On the name of Blastica, you must kill Baron Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lady, you can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Master Glode, my beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on a bit longer. l shall fulfill your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, l shall offer up my body to fulfill the legend of Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Braija...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lija...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gassha...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand that for me to summon you here, your opponent is quite formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,l should sure hope so, for your sake, Desleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,l figured you must be rather bored collecting dust in the Death Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting Baron Zeke should be a perfect way to pass the time for you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Baron Zeke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,lnteresting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,New participants?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This just got interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,l know not what you're plotting, but l'll tell you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't force me to stain my sword with your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we let that outburst go unpunished?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that woman warrior appear to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like she'd make a nice shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,lndeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,l just feel so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Peauvoir and Master Lony, l presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Balenheim is waiting for you in a special viewing chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come with me. l will escort you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Polarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you just sitting there for? Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,l brought you cleansing incense prior to your fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it has a magnificent bouquet. Almost as if you're in Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,l told you, its scent will take you to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,lmpossible... l'm powerless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got quite a powerful mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm starting to really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,l will not forgive this disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Any objection to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here l come, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? ls that all the strength the legendary Baron Zeke has?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,l can feel it, dark energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Desleen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,l gave him a special invitation. He's one of the Three Death Realm swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Death Realm swordsmen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no choice but to keep fighting until you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take one step out of the ring and your friends' lives are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight with all you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're in big trouble if you don't undo these shackles this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea who l am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm Countess Polarine du Peauvoir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My late husband was very strong influential with all the Council members!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can hear you, so save your breath, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He stopped me with the tip of his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Baron Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, just perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick l've put in place would be all for naught if you died in the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,l've got big expectations for you in the next round, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Polarine...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh, be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm one of the Three Death Realm Swordsmen, Gassha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,lmpressive work, defeating Braija.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,l barely lifted a finger against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,l won't go so easily, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Death Sword l brought with me from the Death Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle against your Holy Broadsword shall prove interesting indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're not hostages after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:24:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,lt means they have no intention of letting us survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,l won't be able to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.28,0:24:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you've been there and back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.94,0:24:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, l guess l did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.67,0:24:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in danger if you let me suck your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.01,0:24:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.91,0:24:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your true power... Use it now or you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.50,0:25:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.67,0:25:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y..You saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.94,0:25:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All those upon this fortress shall die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.88,0:25:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a soul will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.78,0:25:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.48,0:25:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggle all you want, but your fate is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.46,0:25:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have a deathwish, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.90,0:25:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, in that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.00,0:25:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,l shall grant that wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.17,0:25:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Baron! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.74,0:25:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Baron! We're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.18,0:26:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! The Count is up to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.28,0:26:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, something came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.39,0:26:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.79,0:26:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You think l'd leave without saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.59,0:26:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.31,0:26:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, woman warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.71,0:26:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did being reminded of your femininity get your heart pumping?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.42,0:26:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.45,0:26:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.46,0:26:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You enjoyed those womanly pleasures before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.80,0:26:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,l thought l told you not to do anything that would make me stain my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.54,0:26:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you gonna do to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.94,0:27:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm not letting you, nor the Count, leave here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.32,0:27:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll show you what you wanted to see: my sword's true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.23,0:27:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,l won't hold back either, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.90,0:27:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.43,0:27:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret technique, Jet-Black Blade! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.99,0:27:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.20,0:28:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.81,0:28:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lose the ability to move your body now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.42,0:28:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,l really hate to kill you, but this is just so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.55,0:28:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end for you, brave woman warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.89,0:28:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.30,0:28:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Th..That thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.92,0:28:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.15,0:28:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,l just need to rest for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.64,0:29:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Desleen!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.60,0:29:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the entertaining trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.67,0:29:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my next opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.64,0:29:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.34,0:29:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,l've already absorbed all the light energy, which supports this fortress, into my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.75,0:29:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that its energy has been sapped, it will fall from the sky any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.22,0:29:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it and all the Council members on it will crash into the middle of Crossland.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.89,0:29:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's the final trick you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.86,0:29:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.30,0:29:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the impressive story.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.66,0:29:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the power that Blastica has given me, this fortress means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.97,0:29:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it, Zeke?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.77,0:29:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay with me and become my ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.51,0:29:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With the magic of Blastica within you, you'll feel pleasures beyond comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.48,0:29:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman's body can be quite a nice place, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.82,0:30:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an attractive woman, Desleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.12,0:30:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, you're not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.32,0:30:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.69,0:30:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to die along with everyone on this fortress then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.10,0:30:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,l'd like to pass on that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.94,0:30:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the fortress has begun plummeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.04,0:30:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it gonna be, Lord Zeke?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.79,0:30:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This... The fortress is falling from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.26,0:30:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can stop it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.43,0:30:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No. l, Baron Zeke, will stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.94,0:30:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.77,0:30:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm sure one of Blastica's followers has heard of the Jet-Black Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.74,0:30:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.63,0:31:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me, Desleen!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.30,0:31:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Bahn, the devil which dwells in the jet-black eyes of Dark Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.41,0:31:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come unto the mortal realm, and make me one with thy blood and flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.55,0:32:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! lt's the Jet-Black Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.48,0:32:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.49,0:32:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Good luck, Lord Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.29,0:32:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm right with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.13,0:32:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as my life is one with the Jet-Black Devil,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.80,0:32:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Blastica's goals will be null and void!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.66,0:32:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,l've absorbed all of this fortress's energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.10,0:32:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is stronger than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.37,0:32:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're about to understand just what true power is!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.37,0:32:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.55,0:32:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.55,0:32:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.39,0:32:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Did you bear witness to Blastica's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.43,0:33:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,lmpossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.18,0:33:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power is nothing compared to mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.89,0:33:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's just an illusion covering up your true weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.43,0:33:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.07,0:33:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running out of time. l'm going to end this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.14,0:33:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,l was just thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.81,0:33:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the black flames of my wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.56,0:33:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Receive my ultimate death blade technique:
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.56,0:34:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Bringer!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.07,0:34:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.52,0:34:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.59,0:34:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, this isn't exactly a cause for celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.22,0:34:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry, Lord Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.71,0:34:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The fortress! lt's gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.93,0:35:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blue Skies Fortress is going back to the sky where it belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.20,0:35:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Desleen,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.01,0:35:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,your soul will never rise to the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.38,0:35:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.58,0:36:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Baron Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.02,0:36:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,l know he's not planning on leaving us here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.56,0:36:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way the Lord Baron would ever forget about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.64,0:36:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He did!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.31,0:36:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Baron! Come and get us!